# <a name="sensitive-information-type-entity-definitions"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-104">Определения типов конфиденциальной информации</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-104">Sensitive information type entity definitions</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-105">Защита от потери данных (DLP) в центре соответствия требованиям включает множество типов конфиденциальной информации, готовых к использованию в политиках защиты от потери данных.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-105">Data loss prevention (DLP) in the Compliance Center includes many sensitive information types that are ready for you to use in your DLP policies.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-106">В этой статье перечислены все эти типы конфиденциальной информации и показано, каким именно образом политика защиты от потери данных выявляет каждый тип.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-106">This topic lists all of these sensitive information types and shows what a DLP policy looks for when it detects each type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-107">Тип конфиденциальной информации определяется шаблоном, который можно идентифицировать регулярным выражением или функцией.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-107">A sensitive information type is defined by a pattern that can be identified by a regular expression or a function.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-108">Кроме того, для идентификации типа конфиденциальной информации могут использоваться подкрепляющие доказательства, такие как ключевые слова и контрольные суммы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-108">In addition, corroborative evidence such as keywords and checksums can be used to identify a sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-109">Уровень вероятности и расположение слов и знаков также используются в процессе оценки.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-109">Confidence level and proximity are also used in the evaluation process.</span></span>
  
## <a name="aba-routing-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-110">Номер маршрутизации код банка ABA</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-110">ABA routing number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-111">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-111">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-112">девять цифр, которые могут быть в форматированном или неформатированном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-112">nine digits which may be in a formatted or unformatted pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-113">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-113">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-114">Форматируемые</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-114">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-115">четыре цифры, начинающиеся с 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7 или 8.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-115">four digits beginning with 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7, or 8</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-116">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-116">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-117">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-117">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-118">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-118">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-119">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-119">a digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-120">Неформатированный: девять последовательных цифр, начиная с 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7 или 8.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-120">Unformatted: nine consecutive digits beginning with 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7, or 8</span></span> 

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-121">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-121">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-122">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-122">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-123">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-123">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-124">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-124">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-125">функция Func_aba_routing находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-125">The function Func_aba_routing finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-126">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ABA_Routing.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-126">A keyword from Keyword_ABA_Routing is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- ABA Routing Number -->
<Entity id="cb353f78-2b72-4c3c-8827-92ebe4f69fdf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_aba_routing" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ABA_Routing" />
      </Pattern>
 </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-140">американбанкассоЦиатионраутингнумбер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-140">americanbankassociationroutingnumber</span></span>

## <a name="argentina-national-identity-dni-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-146">Внутренний идентификационный номер (DNI), Аргентина</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-146">Argentina national identity (DNI) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-147">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-147">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-148">Восемь цифр, разделенных точками.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-148">Eight digits separated by periods</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-149">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-149">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-150">Восемь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-150">Eight digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-151">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-151">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-152">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-152">a period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-153">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-153">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-154">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-154">a period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-155">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-155">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-156">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-156">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-157">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-157">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-158">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-158">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-159">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-159">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-160">регулярное выражение Regex_argentina_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-160">The regular expression Regex_argentina_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-161">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_argentina_national_id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-161">A keyword from Keyword_argentina_national_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Argentina National Identity (DNI) Number -->
<Entity id="eefbb00e-8282-433c-8620-8f1da3bffdb2" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Regex_argentina_national_id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_argentina_national_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-162">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-162">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_argentina_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-163">Keyword_argentina_national_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-163">Keyword_argentina_national_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-166">Идентификация национальной идентификационной карточки</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-166">Identification National Identity Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-167">DNI</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-167">DNI</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-168">Национальная реестр пользователей NIC</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-168">NIC National Registry of Persons</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-169">Documento Nacional de Identidad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-169">Documento Nacional de Identidad</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-171">идентидад</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-171">Identidad</span></span>

## <a name="australia-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-173">Номер банковского счета для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-173">Australia bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-174">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-174">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-175">шесть – ТВН цифрами с номером филиала банка или без него</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-175">six to twn digits with or without a bank state branch number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-176">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-176">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-177">Номер счета — от шести до десяти цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-177">Account number is six to ten digits.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-178">Номер филиала государственного банка Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-178">Australia bank state branch number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-179">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-179">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-180">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-180">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-181">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-181">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-182">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-182">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-183">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-183">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-184">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-184">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-185">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-185">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-186">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-186">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern..</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-187">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-187">A keyword from Keyword_australia_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-188">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-188">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-189">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-189">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-190">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-190">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern..</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-191">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-191">A keyword from Keyword_australia_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="74a54de9-2a30-4aa0-a8aa-3d9327fc07c7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb" />
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_bank_account_number" />
  </Pattern>
 </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-192">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-192">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_australia_bank_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-193">Keyword_australia_bank_account_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-193">Keyword_australia_bank_account_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-194">swift bank code</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-194">swift bank code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-195">correspondent bank</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-195">correspondent bank</span></span>

## <a name="australia-business-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-207">Бизнес-номер Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-207">Australia business number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-208">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-208">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-209">11 цифр с необязательными ограничителями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-209">11 digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-210">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-210">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-211">11 цифр с необязательными ограничителями:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-211">11 digits with optional delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-212">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-212">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-213">Необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-213">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-214">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-214">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-215">Необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-215">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-216">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-216">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-217">Необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-217">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-218">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-218">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-219">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-219">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-220">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-220">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-221">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-221">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-222">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-222">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-223">Функция Func_australian_business_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-223">The function Func_australian_business_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-224">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_australian_business_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-224">A keyword from Keywords_australian_business_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-225">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-225">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-226">Функция Func_australian_business_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-226">The function Func_australian_business_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Australia Business Number -->
      <Entity id="76e83b3b-01ee-4530-aced-e667a6609f49" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_business_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_australian_business_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_business_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-227">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-227">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_australia_business_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-228">Keyword_australia_business_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-228">Keyword_australia_business_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-229">Бизнес-деятельность Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-229">australia business no</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-231">абн #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-231">abn#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-232">бусинессид #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-232">businessid#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-233">Идентификатор бизнеса</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-233">business id</span></span>

## <a name="australia-company-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-236">Номер компании Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-236">Australia company number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-237">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-237">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-238">девять цифр с разделителями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-238">nine digits with delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-239">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-239">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-240">девять цифр с разделителями:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-240">nine digits with delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-241">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-241">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-242">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-242">a space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-243">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-243">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-244">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-244">a space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-245">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-245">three digits</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-246">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-246">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-247">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-247">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-248">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-248">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-249">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-249">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-250">Функция Func_Australian_Company_Number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-250">The function Func_Australian_Company_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-251">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_Australian_Company_Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-251">A keyword from Keyword_Australian_Company_Number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-252">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-252">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-253">Функция Func_Australian_Company_Number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-253">The function Func_Australian_Company_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Australia Company Number -->
      <Entity id="b1fba4f7-7b3e-4bb9-8f9a-9366df604dbb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Australian_Company_Number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Australian_Company_Number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Australian_Company_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="australia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-263">Номер водительского удостоверения для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-263">Australia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-264">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-264">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-265">девять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-265">nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-266">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-266">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-267">девять букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-267">nine letters and digits:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-268">две цифры или буквы (без учета регистра).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-268">two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-269">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-269">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-270">пять цифр или букв (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-270">five digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-271">OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-271">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-272">один-два необязательных буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-272">one to two optional letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-273">от четырех до девяти цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-273">four to nine digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-274">OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-274">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-275">девять цифр или букв (без учета регистра);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-275">nine digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-276">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-276">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-277">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-277">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-278">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-278">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-279">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-279">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-280">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-280">The regular expression Regex_australia_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-281">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-281">A keyword from Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-282">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions не находится.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-282">No keyword from Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Drivers License Number -->
<Entity id="1cbbc8f5-9216-4392-9eb5-5ac2298d1356" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-296">Drivers Lic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-296">Drivers Lic</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-297">Drivers Lics</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-297">Drivers Lics</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-298">Drivers Licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-298">Drivers Licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-299">Drivers Licences</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-299">Drivers Licences</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-300">Driver ' LIC</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-300">Driver'Lic</span></span>

## <a name="australia-medical-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-382">Номер медицинской учетной записи Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-382">Australia medical account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-383">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-383">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-384">10–11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-384">10-11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-385">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-385">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-386">10–11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-386">10-11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-387">Первая цифра находится в диапазоне 2-6</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-387">first digit is in the range 2-6</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-388">девятая цифра — это контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-388">ninth digit is a check digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-389">Десятая цифра — это цифра, связанная с вопросом</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-389">tenth digit is the issue digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-390">Одиннадцатая цифра (необязательно) — индивидуальный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-390">eleventh digit (optional) is the individual number</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-391">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-391">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-392">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-392">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-393">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-393">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-394">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-394">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-395">функция Func_australian_medical_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-395">The function Func_australian_medical_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-396">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-396">A keyword from Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-397">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-397">The checksum passes.</span></span>


```xml
  <!-- Australia Medical Account Number -->
<Entity id="104a99a0-3d3b-4542-a40d-ab0b9e1efe63" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_medical_account_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number"/>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-400">bank account details</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-400">bank account details</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-403">bank payments</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-403">bank payments</span></span>

## <a name="australia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-409">Номер паспорта для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-409">Australia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-410">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-410">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-411">Буква, за которой следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-411">A letter followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-412">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-412">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-413">Буква (без учета регистра), за которой следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-413">A letter (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-414">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-414">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-415">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-415">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-416">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-416">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-417">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-417">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-418">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-418">The regular expression Regex_australia_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-419">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_passport или Keyword_australia_passport_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-419">A keyword from Keyword_passport or Keyword_australia_passport_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Passport Number -->
<Entity id="29869db6-602d-4853-ab93-3484f905df50" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_passport_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_passport_number" />
        </Any>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>   
```

## <a name="australia-tax-file-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-453">Номер файла налога для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-453">Australia tax file number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-454">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-454">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-455">от восьми до девяти цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-455">eight to nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-456">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-456">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-457">от восьми до девяти цифр, как правило, представляются пробелы следующим образом:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-457">eight to nine digits typically presented with spaces as follows:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-458">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-458">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-459">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-459">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-460">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-460">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-461">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-461">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-462">две и три цифры, где последняя цифра — проверочная.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-462">two to three digits where the last digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-463">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-463">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-464">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-464">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-465">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-465">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-466">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-466">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-467">функция Func_australian_tax_file_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-467">The function Func_australian_tax_file_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-468">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number или Keyword_number_exclusions не найдено;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-468">No keyword from Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number or Keyword_number_exclusions is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-469">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-469">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
   <!-- Australia Tax File Number -->
    <Entity id="e29bc95f-ff70-4a37-aa01-04d17360a4c5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_tax_file_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-481">Номер водительского удостоверения для Австрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-481">Austria driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-482">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-482">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-483">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-483">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-484">восемь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-484">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-485">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-485">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-486">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-486">eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-487">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-487">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-488">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-488">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-489">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-489">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-490">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-490">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-491">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-491">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-492">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-492">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
<!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-509">Австрийская идентификационная карточка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-509">Austria identity card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-510">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-510">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-511">24 – символическое сочетание букв, цифр и специальных символов;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-511">A 24-character combination of letters, digits, and special characters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-512">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-512">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-513">24 символа:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-513">24 characters:</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-514">22 буквы (без учета регистра), цифры, обратные косые черты, косые черты и знаки плюса</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-514">22 letters (not case-sensitive), digits, backslashes, forward slashes, or plus signs</span></span> 
    
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-515">две буквы (без учета регистра), цифры, обратные косые черты, знаки косой черты, знаки плюса и знаки равенства.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-515">two letters (not case-sensitive), digits, backslashes, forward slashes, plus signs, or equal signs</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-516">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-516">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-517">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-517">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-518">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-518">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-519">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-519">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-520">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-520">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-521">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-521">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
   
```xml
      <!-- Austria Identity Card -->
      <Entity id="5ec06c3b-007e-4820-8343-7ff73b889735" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-522">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-522">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-526">персоналаусвеис Републик öстерреич</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-526">personalausweis republik österreich</span></span>

## <a name="austria-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-527">Номер паспорта для Австрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-527">Austria passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-528">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе сенситивеинформатион Passport Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-528">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitiveinformation type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-529">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-529">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-530">Одна буква, за которой следует необязательный пробел и семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-530">One letter followed by an optional space and seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-531">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-531">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-532">Сочетание одной буквы, семи цифр и одного пробела:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-532">A combination of one letter, seven digits, and one space:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-533">одна буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-533">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-534">один пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-534">one space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-535">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-535">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-536">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-536">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-537">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-537">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-538">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-538">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-539">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-539">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-540">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-540">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-541">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-541">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-542">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-542">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_austria_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-543">Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-543">Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-544">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-544">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-545">Австрийский номер паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-545">austrian passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-546">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-546">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-547">реисепасс</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-547">reisepass</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-548">öстерреичисч реисепасс</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-548">österreichisch reisepass</span></span>

## <a name="austria-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-549">Австрийский номер социального страхования или эквивалентная идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-549">Austria social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-550">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в номере социального страхования ЕС или эквивалентного идентификатора.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-550">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-551">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-551">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-552">10 цифр в указанном формате</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-552">10 digits in the specified format</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-553">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-553">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-554">10 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-554">10 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-555">три цифры, соответствующие серийному номеру.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-555">three digits that correspond to a serial number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-556">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-556">one check digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-557">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (ДДММГГ —)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-557">six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-558">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-558">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-559">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-559">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-560">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-560">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-561">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-561">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-562">Функция "Func_austria_eu_</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-562">The function  \`Func_austria_eu_</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-563">_or_equivalent ' находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-563">_or_equivalent\` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-564">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-564">a keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-565">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-565">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-566">Функция  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-566">The function  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
            <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-579">созиалверсичерунгснуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-579">sozialversicherungsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-580">созиале сичерхеит Кеин</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-580">soziale sicherheit kein</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-581">версичерунгснуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-581">versicherungsnummer</span></span>

## <a name="austria-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-582">Налоговый идентификационный номер для Австрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-582">Austria tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-583">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-583">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-584">девять цифр с необязательным дефисом и косой чертой.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-584">nine digits with optional hyphen and forward slash</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-585">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-585">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-586">девять цифр с необязательным дефисом и косой чертой.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-586">nine digits with optional hyphen and forward slash:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-587">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-587">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-588">дефис (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-588">a hyphen (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-589">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-589">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-590">косая черта (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-590">a forward slash (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-591">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-591">four digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-592">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-592">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-593">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-593">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-594">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-594">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-595">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-595">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-596">Функция  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-596">The function  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-597">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-597">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-598">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-598">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-599">Функция  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-599">The function  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="4fd58d22-af28-4451-b18a-6f722430a56d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-613">таксидно #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-613">taxidno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-614">таксиднумбер #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-614">taxidnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-615">таксно #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-615">taxno#</span></span>

## <a name="austria-value-added-tax"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-622">Налог на добавленную стоимость (Австрия)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-622">Austria value added tax</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-623">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-623">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-624">11-буквенно-буквенно-буквенный шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-624">11-character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-625">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-625">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-626">11-буквенно-цифровой буквенно-значный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-626">11-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-627">A или a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-627">A or a</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-628">T или t</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-628">T or t</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-629">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-629">Optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-630">U или u</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-630">U or u</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-631">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-631">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-632">две или три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-632">two or three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-633">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-633">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-634">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-634">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-635">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-635">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-636">одна или две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-636">one or two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-637">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-637">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-638">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-638">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-639">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-639">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-640">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-640">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-641">Функция Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-641">The function Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-642">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_Austria_Value_Added_Tax.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-642">A keyword from Keyword_Austria_Value_Added_Tax is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-643">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-643">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-644">Функция Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-644">The function Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Austria Value Added Tax -->
      <Entity id="b6a3eda2-c56c-4b69-a5f7-dca34db00f48" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Austria_Value_Added_Tax" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-documentdb-auth-key"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-662">Ключ проверки подлинности Azure DocumentDB</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-662">Azure DocumentDB auth key</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-663">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-663">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-664">Строка "DocumentDb", за которой следуют символы и строки, описанные в приведенном ниже шаблоне.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-664">The string "DocumentDb" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-665">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-665">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-666">Строка "DocumentDb"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-666">The string "DocumentDb"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-667">Любая комбинация из 3-200 прописных или строчных букв, цифр, символов, специальных символов и пробелов.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-667">Any combination of between 3-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-668">Символ "больше" (>), знак равенства (=), кавычки (") или апостроф (')</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-668">A greater than symbol (>), an equal sign (=), a quotation mark ("), or an apostrophe (')</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-669">Любая комбинация 86 строчных или прописных букв, цифр, символов косой черты (/) или знака плюса (+).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-669">Any combination of 86 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-670">Два знака равенства (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-670">Two equal signs (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-671">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-671">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-672">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-672">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-673">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-673">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-674">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-674">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-675">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureDocumentDBAuthKey находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-675">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureDocumentDBAuthKey finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-676">Регулярное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords не **находит содержимое** , которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-676">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Azure Document DB Auth Key -->
<Entity id="0f587d92-eb28-44a9-bd1c-90f2892b47aa" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureDocumentDBAuthKey" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
          </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-693">Строка "Server", "Server" или "Data Source", за которой следуют символы и строки, описанные в приведенном ниже шаблоне, в том числе строку "клаудапп. Azure".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-693">The string "Server", "server", or "data source" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the string "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-694">com "или" клаудапп. Azure.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-694">com" or "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-695">NET "или" Database. Windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-695">net" or "database.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-696">NET ", а также строку" Password "или" Password "или" pwd ".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-696">net", and the string "Password" or "password" or "pwd".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-697">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-697">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-698">строка "Server", "Server" или "Data Source"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-698">the string "Server", "server", or "data source"</span></span>

Azure.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-703">The string "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-704">com "," клаудапп. Azure.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-704">com", "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-705">NET "или" Database. Windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-705">net", or "database.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-706">команде</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-706">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-707">Любая комбинация из 1-300 прописных или строчных букв, цифр, символов, специальных символов и пробелов.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-707">any combination of between 1-300 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-708">строка "Password", "Password" или "pwd"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-708">the string "Password", "password", or "pwd"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-709">ноль — два символа пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-709">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-710">знак равенства (=);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-710">an equal sign (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-714">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-714">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-715">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-715">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-716">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-716">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-717">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-717">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-718">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureConnectionString находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-718">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-719">Регулярное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords не **находит содержимое** , которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-719">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-iot-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-734">Строка подключения Azure IoT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-734">Azure IoT connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-735">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-735">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-736">Строка "HostName", за которой следуют символы и строки, описанные в приведенном ниже шаблоне, включая строки "Azure — Devices.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-736">The string "HostName" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the strings "azure-devices.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-737">NET "и" Шаредакцесскэй ".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-737">net" and "SharedAccessKey".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-738">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-738">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-739">строка "HostName"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-739">the string "HostName"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-740">ноль — два символа пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-740">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-741">знак равенства (=);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-741">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-742">ноль — два символа пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-742">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-743">Любая комбинация из 1-200 прописных или строчных букв, цифр, символов, специальных символов и пробелов.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-743">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-744">строка "Azure — Devices.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-744">the string "azure-devices.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-745">команде</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-745">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-746">Любая комбинация из 1-200 прописных или строчных букв, цифр, символов, специальных символов и пробелов.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-746">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-747">строка "Шаредакцесскэй"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-747">the string "SharedAccessKey"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-748">ноль — два символа пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-748">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-749">знак равенства (=);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-749">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-750">ноль — два символа пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-750">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-751">Любая комбинация 43 строчных или прописных букв, цифр, символов косой черты (/) или знака плюса (+).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-751">any combination of 43 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-752">знак равенства (=);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-752">an equal sign (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-753">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-753">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-754">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-754">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-755">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-755">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-756">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-756">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-757">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureIoTConnectionString находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-757">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureIoTConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-758">Регулярное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords не **находит содержимое** , которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-758">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure IoT Connection String-->
<Entity id="0b34bec3-d5d6-4974-b7b0-dcdb5c90c29d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureIoTConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-767">localhost</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-767">localhost</span></span>
