- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4549">National ID Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4549">National ID Number</span></span>
   
## <a name="italy-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4550">Номер водительского удостоверения для Италии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4550">Italy driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4551">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4551">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4552">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4552">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4553">сочетание из 10 букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4553">a combination of 10 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4554">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4554">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4555">сочетание из 10 букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4555">a combination of 10 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4556">одна буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4556">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4557">буква "A" или "V" (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4557">the letter "A" or "V" (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4558">семь букв (без учета регистра), цифр или символ подчеркивания.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4558">seven letters (not case sensitive), digits, or the underscore character</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4559">одна буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4559">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4560">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4560">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4561">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4561">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4562">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4562">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4563">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4563">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4564">регулярное выражение Regex_italy_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4564">The regular expression Regex_italy_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4565">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4565">A keyword from Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Italy Driver's license Number -->
<Entity id="97d6244f-9157-41bd-8e0c-9d669a5c4d71" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_drivers_license_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4566">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4566">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_italy_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4567">Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4567">Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4568">numero di patente di guida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4568">numero di patente di guida</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4569">patente di guida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4569">patente di guida</span></span> 

## <a name="italy-fiscal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4570">Финансовый код Италии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4570">Italy fiscal code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4571">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4571">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4572">16 – символическое сочетание букв и цифр в указанном шаблоне.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4572">a 16-character combination of letters and digits in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4573">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4573">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4574">16 – буквенное сочетание букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4574">A 16-character combination of letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4575">три буквы, соответствующие первым трем согласным в имени семейства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4575">three letters that correspond to the first three consonants in the family name</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4576">три буквы, соответствующие первым, третьим и четвертым согласным в имени.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4576">three letters that correspond to the first, third, and fourth consonants in the first name</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4577">две цифры, соответствующие последним цифрам года рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4577">two digits that correspond to the last digits of the birth year</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4578">одна буква, соответствующая букве дня рождения, буквы используются в алфавитном порядке, но используются только буквы от A до E, H, L, M, P, R — T (то есть Январь — это R, а Октябрь — R)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4578">one letter that corresponds to the letter for the month of birth—letters are used in alphabetical order, but only the letters A to E, H, L, M, P, R to T are used (thus, January is A and October is R)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4579">две цифры, которые соответствуют дню месяца рождения, для различения пола, 40 добавляется в день рождения для женщин</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4579">two digits that correspond to the day of the month of birth—in order to differentiate between genders, 40 is added to the day of birth for women</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4580">четыре цифры, соответствующие коду города, который относится к органу государственной власти, в котором был создан пользователь, (для иностранных стран используются коды уровня страны).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4580">four digits that corresponds to the area code specific to the municipality where the person was born (country-wide codes are used for foreign countries)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4581">одна цифра четности</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4581">one parity digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4582">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4582">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4583">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4583">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4584">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4584">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4585">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4585">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4586">Функция  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4586">The function  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4587">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4587">A keyword from  `Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4588">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4588">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4589">Функция  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4589">The function  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Italy Fiscal Code -->
      <Entity id="4cd79172-8da9-4ff5-9188-98b1e7e2eca6" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4595">Персональные подкодеки</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4595">codice personale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4596">Финансовый код</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4596">fiscal code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4597">Нумеро цертификато персональный</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4597">numero certificato personale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4598">Нумеро di идентификазионе Фин.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4598">numero di identificazione fiscale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4599">личный идентификатор нумеро</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4599">numero id personale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4600">персональные настройки нумеро</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4600">numero personale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4601">личный номер сертификата</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4601">personal certificate number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4602">персональный код</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4602">personal code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4603">личный код</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4603">personal id code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4604">личный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4604">personal id number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4605">персоналкодено #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4605">personalcodeno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4606">Налоговый код</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4606">tax code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4607">tax id
</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4607">tax id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4608">Налоговый идентификатор</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4608">tax identification no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4609">идентификационный номер налога</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4609">tax identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4610">идентификационный номер налогоплательщика</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4610">tax identity number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4611">налог без #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4611">tax no#</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4613">Налоговый номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4613">tax number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4614">Регистрационный номер налогоплательщика</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4614">tax registration number</span></span>

## <a name="italy-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4624">Номер паспорта для Италии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4624">Italy passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4625">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4625">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4626">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4626">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4627">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4627">two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4628">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4628">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4629">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4629">two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4630">две цифры или буквы (без учета регистра).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4630">two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4631">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4631">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4632">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4632">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4633">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4633">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4634">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4634">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4635">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4635">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4636">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4636">The regular expression  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4637">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4637">A keyword from  `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4642">пассапорто</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4642">passaporto</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4643">пассапорто итальянский</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4643">passaporto italiana</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4644">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4644">passport number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4646">пассапорто нумеро</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4646">passaporto numero</span></span>

## <a name="italy-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4649">Налоговый номер добавленной стоимости (Италия)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4649">Italy value added tax number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4650">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4650">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4651">13-буквенно-цифровой буквенный шаблон с необязательными ограничителями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4651">13 character alphanumeric pattern with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4652">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4652">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4653">13-буквенно-цифровой буквенно-цифровой шаблон с необязательными ограничителями:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4653">13 character alphanumeric pattern with optional delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4654">I или i</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4654">I or i</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4655">T или t</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4655">T or t</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4656">необязательный пробел, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4656">optional space, dot, hyphen or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4657">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4657">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4658">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4658">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4659">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4659">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4660">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4660">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4661">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4661">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4662">Функция Func_italy_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4662">The function Func_italy_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4663">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4663">A keyword from Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4664">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4664">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4665">Функция Func_italy_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4665">The function Func_italy_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Italy Value Added Tax -->
      <Entity id="26a8cc07-2283-4a2a-ab1d-4ab643c4c67f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4673">Номер банковского счета для Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4673">Japan bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4674">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4674">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4675">семь или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4675">seven or eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4676">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4676">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4677">номер банковского счета:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4677">bank account number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4678">семь или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4678">seven or eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4679">код филиала банковского счета:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4679">bank account branch code:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4680">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4680">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4681">пробел или тире (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4681">a space or dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4682">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4682">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4683">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4683">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4684">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4684">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4685">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4685">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4686">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4686">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4687">Функция Func_jp_bank_account находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4687">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4688">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4688">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4689">Верно одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4689">One of the following is true:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4690">функция Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4690">The function Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4691">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4691">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4692">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4692">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4693">функция Func_jp_bank_account находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4693">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4694">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4694">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="d354f95b-96ee-4b80-80bc-4377312b55bc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Version minEngineVersion="15.01.0131.000">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code" />
          </Any>
      </Pattern>
  </Version>    
     <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_jp_bank_account"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4696">Keyword_jp_bank_account</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4696">Keyword_jp_bank_account</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4701">Checking Acct #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4701">Checking Acct #</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4702">Checking Acct No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4702">Checking Acct No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4703">Checking Account No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4703">Checking Account No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4704">Bank Account Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4704">Bank Account Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4705">Bank Account</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4705">Bank Account</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4706">Bank Account #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4706">Bank Account #</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4707">Bank Acct Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4707">Bank Acct Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4708">Bank Acct #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4708">Bank Acct #</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4709">Bank Acct No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4709">Bank Acct No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4710">Bank Account No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4710">Bank Account No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4711">Savings Account Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4711">Savings Account Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4712">Savings Account</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4712">Savings Account</span></span>

## <a name="japan-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4753">Номер водительского удостоверения для Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4753">Japan driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4754">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4754">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4755">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4755">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4756">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4756">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4757">12 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4757">12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4758">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4758">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4759">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4759">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4760">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4760">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4761">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4761">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4762">функция Func_jp_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4762">The function Func_jp_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4763">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4763">A keyword from Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="c6011143-d087-451c-8313-7f6d4aed2270" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-my-number---corporate"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4791">Мой номер для Японии — корпоративный</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4791">Japan My Number - Corporate</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4792">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4792">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4793">13 цифра, цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4793">13 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4794">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4794">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4795">13 цифра:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4795">13 digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4796">одна цифра от 1 до девяти</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4796">one digit from one to nine</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4797">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4797">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4798">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4798">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4799">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4799">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4800">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4800">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4801">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4801">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4802">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_corporate находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4802">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4803">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4803">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4804">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4804">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4805">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_corporate находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4805">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Corporate -->
      <Entity id="9e0eaf79-ff20-4ffb-b3e4-e7368d5db6ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-my-number---personal"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4818">Япония мой номер — личное</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4818">Japan My Number - Personal</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4819">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4819">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4820">12 цифр номера</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4820">12 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4821">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4821">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4822">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4822">12 digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4823">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4823">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4824">необязательный пробел, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4824">an optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4825">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4825">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4826">необязательный пробел, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4826">an optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4827">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4827">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4828">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4828">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4829">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4829">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4830">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4830">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4831">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4831">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4832">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_personal находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4832">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4833">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4833">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4834">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4834">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4835">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_personal находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4835">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Personal -->
      <Entity id="98da8e66-7299-4ebd-9f82-c871ab37d3ef" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_personal" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_personal" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4836">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4836">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4838">мой номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4838">my number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4839">マイナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4839">マイナンバー</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4840">個人番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4840">個人番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4841">共通番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4841">共通番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4842">マイナンバーカード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4842">マイナンバーカード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4843">マイナンバーカード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4843">マイナンバーカード番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4844">個人番号カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4844">個人番号カード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4845">個人識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4845">個人識別番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4846">個人識別ナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4846">個人識別ナンバー</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4847">通知カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4847">通知カード</span></span>

   
## <a name="japan-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4848">Номер паспорта для Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4848">Japan passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4849">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4849">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4850">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4850">two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4851">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4851">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4852">две буквы (без учета регистра), за которыми следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4852">two letters (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4853">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4853">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4854">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4854">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4855">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4855">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4856">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4856">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4857">функция Func_jp_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4857">The function Func_jp_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4858">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4858">A keyword from Keyword_jp_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Passport Number -->
<Entity id="75177310-1a09-4613-bf6d-833aae3743f8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_passport" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4859">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4859">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_passport"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4860">Keyword_jp_passport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4860">Keyword_jp_passport</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4861">パスポート</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4861">パスポート</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4862">パスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4862">パスポート番号</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4863">パスポートのнум</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4863">パスポートのNum</span></span>

## <a name="japan-residence-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4865">Номер карточки для Японии (Япония)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4865">Japan residence card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4866">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4866">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4867">12 букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4867">12 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4868">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4868">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4869">12 букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4869">12 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4870">две буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4870">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4871">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4871">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4872">две буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4872">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4873">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4873">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4874">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4874">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4875">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4875">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4876">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4876">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4877">Регулярное выражение Regex_jp_residence_card_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4877">The regular expression Regex_jp_residence_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4878">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_residence_card_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4878">A keyword from Keyword_jp_residence_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Japan Residence Card Number-->
-<Entity id="ac36fef2-a289-4e2c-bb48-b02366e89fc0" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Regex_jp_residence_card_number"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_residence_card_number"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4879">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4879">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_residence_card_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4880">Keyword_jp_residence_card_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4880">Keyword_jp_residence_card_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4881">Номер карточки проживания</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4881">Residence card number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4882">Номер карточки проживания</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4882">Residence card no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4883">Карточка проживания #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4883">Residence card #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4884">在留カード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4884">在留カード番号</span></span>

## <a name="japan-resident-registration-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4885">Номер резидентного регистрационного номера для Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4885">Japan resident registration number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4886">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4886">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4887">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4887">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4888">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4888">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4889">11 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4889">11 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4890">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4890">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4891">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4891">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4892">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4892">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4893">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4893">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4894">функция Func_jp_resident_registration_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4894">The function Func_jp_resident_registration_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4895">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4895">A keyword from Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Resident Registration Number -->
<Entity id="01c1209b-6389-4faf-a5f8-3f7e13899652" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_resident_registration_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4899">Resident Register Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4899">Resident Register Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4900">Residents Basic Registry Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4900">Residents Basic Registry Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4901">Resident Registration No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4901">Resident Registration No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4902">Resident Register No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4902">Resident Register No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4903">Residents Basic Registry No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4903">Residents Basic Registry No.</span></span>

## <a name="japan-social-insurance-number-sin"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4909">Номер социального страхования для Японии (SIN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4909">Japan social insurance number (SIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4910">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4910">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4911">7–12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4911">7-12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4912">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4912">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4913">7–12 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4913">7-12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4914">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4914">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4915">дефис (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4915">a hyphen (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4916">шесть цифр или</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4916">six digits OR</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4917">7–12 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4917">7-12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4918">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4918">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4919">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4919">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4920">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4920">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4921">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4921">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4922">функция Func_jp_sin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4922">The function Func_jp_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4923">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_sin.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4923">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4924">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4924">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4925">функция Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4925">The function Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4926">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_sin.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4926">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Social Insurance Number -->
<Entity id="c840e719-0896-45bb-84fd-1ed5c95e45ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin_pre_1997" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_jp_sin"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4928">Keyword_jp_sin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4928">Keyword_jp_sin</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4929">Social Insurance No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4929">Social Insurance No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4930">Social Insurance Num</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4930">Social Insurance Num</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4931">Social Insurance Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4931">Social Insurance Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4932">社会保険のテンキー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4932">社会保険のテンキー</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4933">社会保険番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4933">社会保険番号</span></span> 

## <a name="latvia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4934">Номер водительского удостоверения для Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4934">Latvia driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4935">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4935">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4936">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4936">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4937">три буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4937">three letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4938">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4938">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4939">три буквы и шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4939">three letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4940">три буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4940">three letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4941">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4941">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4942">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4942">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4943">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4943">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4944">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4944">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4945">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4945">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4946">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4946">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4947">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4947">A keyword from  `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="latvia-personal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4963">Личный код Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4963">Latvia personal code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4964">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4964">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4965">11 цифр и необязательный дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4965">11 digits and an optional hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4966">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4966">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4967">Старый формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4967">Old format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4968">11 цифр и дефис:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4968">11 digits and a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4969">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (ДДММГГ —)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4969">six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4970">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4970">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4971">одна цифра, соответствующая столетию рождения ("0" для 19 века, "1" для 20-й век) и "2" для 21 века)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4971">one digit that corresponds to the century of birth ("0" for 19th century, "1" for 20th century, and "2" for 21st century)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4972">четыре цифры, созданные случайным образом</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4972">four digits, randomly generated</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4973">Новый формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4973">New format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4974">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4974">11 digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4975">Две цифры "32"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4975">Two digits "32"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4976">девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4976">Nine digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4977">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4977">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4978">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4978">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4979">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4979">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4980">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4980">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4981">Функция  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` или регулярное выражение `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` выполняет поиск содержимого, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4981">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` or the regex `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4982">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4982">A keyword from  `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4983">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4983">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-4984">Функция  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` или регулярное выражение `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` выполняет поиск содержимого, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-4984">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` or the regex `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Personal Code -->
      <Entity id="03fcf763-27c2-49ed-9422-2641c6c895c9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="latvia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5047">Номер паспорта для Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5047">Latvia passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5048">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5048">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5049">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5049">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5050">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5050">two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5051">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5051">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5052">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5052">two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5053">две цифры или буквы (без учета регистра).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5053">two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5054">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5054">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5055">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5055">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5056">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5056">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5057">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5057">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5058">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5058">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5059">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5059">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5060">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5060">A keyword from  `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5061">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5061">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5062">Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5062">Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5063">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5063">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5064">номер паспорта для Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5064">latvian passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5065">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5065">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5066">ПАСЕ нумурс</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5066">pase numurs</span></span>    


## <a name="lithuania-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5067">Литва номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5067">Lithuania driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5068">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5068">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5069">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5069">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5070">восемь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5070">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5071">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5071">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5072">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5072">eight digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5073">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5073">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5074">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5074">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5075">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5075">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5076">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5076">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5077">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5077">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5078">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5078">A keyword from  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

#### <a name="keywords_lithuania_eu_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5080">Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver "s_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5080">Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5083">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5083">driver license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5084">Лицензия на драйвер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5084">driver licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5085">Drivers лик.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5085">drivers lic.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5088">driver's license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5088">driver's license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5089">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5089">driver's license number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5091">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5091">driving license number</span></span>

## <a name="lithuania-personal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5094">Литва персональный код</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5094">Lithuania personal code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5095">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5095">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5096">11 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5096">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5097">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5097">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5098">11 цифр без пробелов и разделителей:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5098">11 digits without spaces and delimiters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5099">одна цифра (1-6), соответствующая пол и век рождения человека</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5099">one digit (1-6) that corresponds to the person's gender and century of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5100">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (ГГММДД)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5100">six digits that correspond to birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5101">три цифры, которые соответствуют серийному числу даты рождения.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5101">three digits that correspond to the serial number of the date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5102">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5102">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5103">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5103">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5104">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5104">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5105">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5105">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5106">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5106">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5107">Функция  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5107">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5108">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5108">A keyword from  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5109">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5109">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5110">Функция  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5110">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Personal Code -->
      <Entity id="cd6d3786-8ec3-4524-a2cf-1e0095379171" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
