## <a name="lithuania-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5145">Литва номер паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5145">Lithuania passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5146">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5146">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5147">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5147">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5148">восемь цифр или букв без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5148">eight digits or letters with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5149">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5149">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5150">восемь цифр или букв (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5150">eight digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5151">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5151">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5152">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5152">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5153">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5153">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5154">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5154">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5155">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5155">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5156">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5156">A keyword from  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

#### <a name="keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5158">Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5158">Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number</span></span>

## <a name="luxemburg-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5163">Номер водительского удостоверения Луксембург</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5163">Luxemburg driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5164">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5164">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5165">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5165">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5166">шесть цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5166">six digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5167">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5167">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5168">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5168">six digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5169">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5169">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5170">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5170">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5171">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5171">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5172">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5172">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5173">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5173">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5174">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5174">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-national-identification-number-natural-persons"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5190">Национальный идентификационный номер Луксембург (для природных людей)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5190">Luxemburg national identification number (natural persons)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5191">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5191">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5192">13 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5192">13 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5193">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5193">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5194">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5194">13 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5195">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5195">11 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5196">две контрольные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5196">two check digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5197">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5197">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5198">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5198">yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5199">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5199">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5200">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5200">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5201">Функция  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5201">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5202">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5202">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5203">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5203">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5204">Функция  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5204">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 


```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg National Identification Number (Natural persons) -->
      <Entity id="aaf661ed-29ec-426d-8bf9-880cad298ebb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5205">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5205">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5206">Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5206">Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5207">Идентификатор еиндеутиже</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5207">eindeutige id</span></span>

## <a name="luxemburg-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5227">Номер паспорта Луксембург</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5227">Luxemburg passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5228">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5228">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5229">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5229">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5230">восемь цифр или букв без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5230">eight digits or letters with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5231">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5231">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5232">восемь цифр или букв (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5232">eight digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5233">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5233">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5234">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5234">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5235">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5235">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5236">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5236">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5237">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_nation_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5237">The regular expression  `Regex_nation_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5238">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_nation_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5238">A keyword from  `Keywords_nation_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_nation_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_nation_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5239">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5239">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_nation_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5240">Keywords_nation_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5240">Keywords_nation_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5241">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5241">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5242">номер паспорта для Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5242">latvian passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5243">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5243">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5244">пасснуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5244">passnummer</span></span>

## <a name="luxemburg-national-identification-number-non-natural-persons"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5245">Луксембург Национальный идентификационный номер (неестественные пользователи)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5245">Luxemburg national identification number (non natural persons)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5246">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5246">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5247">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5247">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5248">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5248">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5249">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5249">11 digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5250">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5250">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5251">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5251">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5252">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5252">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5253">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5253">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5254">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5254">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5255">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5255">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5256">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5256">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5257">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5257">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5258">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5258">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5259">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5259">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5260">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5260">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5261">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5261">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5262">Функция  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5262">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5263">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5263">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5264">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5264">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5265">Функция  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5265">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg National Identification Number (Non-natural persons) -->
      <Entity id="84bffa3a-d805-4788-a613-b1e4df3804cf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="malaysia-identification-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5305">Идентификационный номер карты Малайзии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5305">Malaysia identification card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5306">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5306">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5307">12 цифр, содержащих необязательные дефисы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5307">12 digits containing optional hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5308">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5308">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5309">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5309">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5310">шесть цифр в формате ГГММДД Дата рождения;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5310">six digits in the format YYMMDD which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5311">тире (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5311">a dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5312">код места рождения из двух букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5312">two-letter place-of-birth code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5313">тире (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5313">a dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5314">три случайные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5314">three random digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5315">код пола из одной цифры;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5315">one-digit gender code</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5316">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5316">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5317">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5317">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5318">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5318">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5319">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5319">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5320">регулярное выражение Regex_malaysia_id_card_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5320">The regular expression Regex_malaysia_id_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5321">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5321">A keyword from Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Malaysia ID Card Number -->
</Entity>
      <Entity id="7f0e921c-9677-435b-aba2-bb8f1013c749" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
            <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malaysia_id_card_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="malta-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5348">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Мальта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5348">Malta driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5349">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5349">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5350">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5350">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5351">Сочетание двух символов и шести цифр в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5351">Combination of two characters and six digits in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5352">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5352">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5353">сочетание двух символов и шести цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5353">combination of two characters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5354">два символа (цифры или буквы без учета регистра);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5354">two characters (digits or letters, not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5355">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5355">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5356">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5356">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5357">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5357">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5358">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5358">three digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5359">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5359">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5360">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5360">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5361">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5361">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5362">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5362">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5363">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5363">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5364">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5364">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
<!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
 <Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5374">driver's license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5374">driver's license</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5377">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5377">driving license number</span></span>

## <a name="malta-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5380">Номер идентификационной карточки Мальта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5380">Malta identity card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5381">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5381">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5382">семь цифр, за которыми следует одна буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5382">seven digits followed by one letter</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5383">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5383">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5384">семь цифр, за которыми следует одна буква:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5384">seven digits followed by one letter:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5385">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5385">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5386">одна буква в письмах "M, G, A, P, L, H, B, Z" (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5386">one letter in "M, G, A, P, L, H, B, Z" (case insensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5387">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5387">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5388">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5388">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5389">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5389">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5390">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5390">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5391">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5391">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5392">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5392">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5393">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5393">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5394">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5394">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Identity Card Number -->
      <Entity id="854b36b3-a388-4ac8-a4ec-677c2b5e4356" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5396">Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5396">Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5401">нумру Ta ' идентификаззжони персонали</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5401">numru ta 'identifikazzjoni personali</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5402">нумру Ta ' идентификаззжони ТАТ такскса</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5402">numru ta 'identifikazzjoni tat-taxxa</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5403">нумру Ta ' идентификаззжони унику</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5403">numru ta 'identifikazzjoni uniku</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5404">нумру Ta ' идентитà унику</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5404">numru ta' identità uniku</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5405">нумруные зада сервизз таċ ċиттадин</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5405">numru tas-servizz taċ-ċittadin</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5406">нумру ТАТ — такскса</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5406">numru tat-taxxa</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5407">персональный числовой код</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5407">personal numeric code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5408">уникальный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5408">unique identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5409">уникальный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5409">unique identity number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5410">уникуеидентитино #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5410">uniqueidentityno#</span></span>


## <a name="malta-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5411">Номер паспорта для Мальта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5411">Malta passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5412">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5412">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5413">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5413">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5414">семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5414">seven digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5415">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5415">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5416">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5416">seven digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5417">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5417">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5418">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5418">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5419">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5419">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5420">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5420">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5421">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5421">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5422">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5422">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5423">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5423">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_malta_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5424">Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5424">Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5425">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5425">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5426">номер паспорта Мальтийский</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5426">maltese passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5427">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5427">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5428">нумру Тал — пассапорт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5428">numru tal-passaport</span></span>

## <a name="malta-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5429">Идентификационный номер налога Мальта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5429">Malta tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5430">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5430">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5431">Для национальных Мальтийский:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5431">For Maltese nationals:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5432">семь цифр и одна буква в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5432">seven digits and one letter in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5433">Мальтийскийные страны и Мальтийский, не являющиеся субъектами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5433">Non-Maltese nationals and Maltese entities:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5434">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5434">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5435">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5435">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5436">Мальтийский Nationals: семь цифр и одна буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5436">Maltese nationals: seven digits and one letter</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5437">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5437">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5438">одна буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5438">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5439">Мальтийскийные страны и Мальтийский, не связанные с организациями: девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5439">Non-Maltese nationals and Maltese entities: nine digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5440">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5440">nine digits</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5441">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5441">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5442">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5442">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5443">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5443">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5444">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5444">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5445">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number`  или `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` ищет содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5445">The regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number`  or `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5446">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5446">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5447">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5447">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5448">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number` или `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` ищет содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5448">The regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number` or `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Tax ID Number -->
      <Entity id="ec830c63-65f4-45d0-9d8c-910dc8334b20" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-citizens-service-bsn-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5481">Номер службы (BSN) для Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5481">Netherlands citizen's service (BSN) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5482">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5482">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5483">восемь девяти цифр, содержащих необязательные пробелы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5483">eight-nine digits containing optional spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5484">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5484">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5485">восемь девяти цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5485">eight-nine digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5486">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5486">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5487">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5487">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5488">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5488">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5489">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5489">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5490">две три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5490">two-three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5491">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5491">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5492">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5492">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5493">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5493">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5494">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5494">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5495">функция Func_netherlands_bsn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5495">The function Func_netherlands_bsn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5496">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_netherlands_bsn;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5496">A keyword from Keyword_netherlands_bsn is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5497">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5497">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Citizen's Service (BSN) Number -->
      <Entity id="c5f54253-ef7e-44f6-a578-440ed67e946d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_bsn" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5498">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5498">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_netherlands_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5499">Keywords_netherlands_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5499">Keywords_netherlands_eu_national_id_card</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5500">BSN #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5500">bsn#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5501">BSN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5501">bsn</span></span>

## <a name="netherlands-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5521">Номер водительского удостоверения для Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5521">Netherlands driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5522">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5522">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5523">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5523">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5524">десять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5524">ten digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5525">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5525">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5526">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5526">ten digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5527">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5527">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5528">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5528">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5529">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5529">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5530">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5530">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5531">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5531">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5532">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5532">A keyword from  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5550">Номер паспорта Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5550">Netherlands passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5551">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5551">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5552">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5552">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5553">девять букв или цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5553">nine letters or digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5554">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5554">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5555">девять букв или цифр;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5555">nine letters or digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5556">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5556">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5557">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5557">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5558">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5558">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5559">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5559">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5560">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5560">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5561">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5561">A keyword from  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5571">Идентификационный номер налога Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5571">Netherlands tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5572">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5572">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5573">девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5573">nine digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5574">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5574">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5575">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5575">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5576">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5576">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5577">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5577">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5578">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5578">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5579">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5579">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5580">Функция  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5580">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5581">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5581">A keyword from  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5582">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5582">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5583">Функция  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5583">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="01f42a64-eba7-4892-a67b-398237e4ade2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5621">Номер налога добавленных значений в Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5621">Netherlands value added tax number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5622">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5622">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5623">14-буквенно-буквенно-цифровой шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5623">14 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5624">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5624">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5625">14-буквенно-буквенно-символьный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5625">14-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5626">N или n</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5626">N or n</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5627">L или l</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5627">L or l</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5628">необязательный пробел, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5628">optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5629">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5629">nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5630">необязательный пробел, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5630">optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5631">B или b</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5631">B or b</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5632">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5632">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5633">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5633">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5634">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5634">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5635">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5635">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5636">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5636">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5637">Функция Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5637">The function Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5638">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5638">A keyword from Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5639">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5639">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5640">Функция Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5640">The function Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="4f320d9b-4972-41ae-b337-88d499bb1ade" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5641">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5641">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_netherlands_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5642">Keyword_netherlands_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5642">Keyword_netherlands_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5643">номер НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5643">vat number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5644">НДС No</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5644">vat no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5645">процент #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5645">vat#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5646">веарде тафоеже налога на жетал</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5646">wearde tafoege tax getal</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5647">БТВ нûмер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5647">btw nûmer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5648">БТВ — нуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5648">btw-nummer</span></span>


## <a name="new-zealand-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5649">Номер банковского счета Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5649">New Zealand bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5650">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5650">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5651">шаблон с 14 до 16 цифр с необязательным разделителем</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5651">14 to 16 digit pattern with optional delimiter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5652">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5652">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5653">шаблон с 14 до 16 цифр с необязательным разделителем:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5653">14 to 16 digit pattern with optional delimiter:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5654">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5654">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5655">Необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5655">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5656">от трех до четырех цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5656">three to four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5657">Необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5657">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5658">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5658">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5659">Необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5659">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5660">две до трех цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5660">two to three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5661">Параметры дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5661">an options hyphen or space</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5662">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5662">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5663">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5663">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5664">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5664">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5665">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5665">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5666">Функция Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5666">The function Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5667">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_new_zealand_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5667">A keyword from Keywords_new_zealand_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5668">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5668">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5669">Функция Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5669">The function Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Bank Account Number -->
      <Entity id="1a97fc2b-dd2f-48f1-bc4e-2ddf25813956" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_new_zealand_bank_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_bank_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5671">Keyword_new_zealand_bank_account_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5671">Keyword_new_zealand_bank_account_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5672">номер счета</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5672">account number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5674">bank_acct_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5674">bank_acct_id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5675">bank_acct_branch</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5675">bank_acct_branch</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5676">bank_acct_nbr</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5676">bank_acct_nbr</span></span>


## <a name="new-zealand-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5677">Номер водительского удостоверения для Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5677">New Zealand driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5678">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5678">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5679">8-буквенно-цифровой шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5679">eight character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5680">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5680">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5681">8-буквенно-цифровой шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5681">eight character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5682">две буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5682">two letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5683">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5683">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5684">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5684">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5685">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5685">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5686">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5686">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5687">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5687">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5688">Функция Func_newzealand_driver_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5688">The function Func_newzealand_driver_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5689">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5689">A keyword from Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5690">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5690">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5691">Функция Func_newzealand_driver_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5691">The function Func_newzealand_driver_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Driver License Number -->
      <Entity id="1924b377-d287-49c9-a737-cfe7a8a2615a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5692">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5692">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5693">Keyword_new_zealand_drivers_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5693">Keyword_new_zealand_drivers_license_number</span></span>

## <a name="new-zealand-inland-revenue-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5758">Номер дохода по некоторому контакту для Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5758">New Zealand inland revenue number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5759">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5759">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5760">восемь или девять цифр с необязательными ограничителями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5760">eight or nine digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5761">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5761">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5762">восемь или девять цифр с необязательными ограничителями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5762">eight or nine digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5763">две или три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5763">two or three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5764">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5764">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5765">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5765">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5766">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5766">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5767">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5767">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5768">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5768">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5769">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5769">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5770">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5770">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5771">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5771">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5772">Функция Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5772">The function Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5773">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5773">A keyword from Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5774">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5774">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5775">Функция Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5775">The function Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Inland Revenue Number -->
      <Entity id="dd0fe2bc-7bcf-455f-bac1-83b1e3eb25fd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5777">Keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5777">Keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5778">ИРД но.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5778">ird no.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5779">ИРД нет #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5779">ird no#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5780">NZ ИРД</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5780">nz ird</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5781">Новая Зеландия ИРД</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5781">new zealand ird</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5782">номер ИРД</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5782">ird number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5783">номер дохода на землю</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5783">inland revenue number</span></span>


## <a name="new-zealand-ministry-of-health-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5784">Номер министерства здоровья Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5784">New Zealand ministry of health number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5785">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5785">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5786">три буквы, пробел (необязательно) и четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5786">three letters, a space (optional), and four digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5787">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5787">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5788">три буквы (без учета регистра), пробел (необязательно) из четырех цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5788">three letters (not case sensitive) a space (optional) four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5789">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5789">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5790">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5790">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5791">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5791">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5792">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5792">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5793">функция Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5793">The function Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5794">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_nz_terms;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5794">A keyword from Keyword_nz_terms is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5795">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5795">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- New Zealand Health Number -->
<Entity id="2b71c1c8-d14e-4430-82dc-fd1ed6bf05c7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_nz_terms" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
