- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5801">обращения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5801">treatment</span></span> 


## <a name="new-zealand-social-wlefare-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5802">Номер социального влефареа Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5802">New Zealand social wlefare number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5803">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5803">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5804">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5804">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5805">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5805">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5806">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5806">nine digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5807">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5807">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5808">Необязательный перенос</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5808">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5809">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5809">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5810">Необязательный перенос</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5810">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5811">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5811">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5812">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5812">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5813">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5813">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5814">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5814">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5815">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5815">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5816">Функция Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5816">The function Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5817">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5817">A keyword from Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5818">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5818">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5819">Функция Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5819">The function Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Newzealand Social Welfare Number -->
      <Entity id="20f3c48d-4ac1-4cd2-86bd-34ecc1826e9d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5820">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5820">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5821">Keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5821">Keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5822">социальные велфаре #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5822">social welfare #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5823">социальные велфаре #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5823">social welfare#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5824">социальное велфаре No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5824">social welfare No.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5825">номер социального велфаре</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5825">social welfare number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5826">свн #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5826">swn#</span></span>

   
## <a name="norway-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5827">Идентификационный номер Норвегии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5827">Norway identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5828">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5828">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5829">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5829">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5830">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5830">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5831">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5831">11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5832">шесть цифр в формате ддммгг — Дата рождения;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5832">six digits in the format DDMMYY which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5833">индивидуальный номер из трех цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5833">three-digit individual number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5834">две контрольные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5834">two check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5835">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5835">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5836">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5836">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5837">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5837">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5838">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5838">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5839">функция Func_norway_id_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5839">The function Func_norway_id_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5840">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_norway_id_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5840">A keyword from Keyword_norway_id_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5841">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5841">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5842">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5842">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5843">функция Func_norway_id_numbe находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5843">The function Func_norway_id_numbe finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5844">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5844">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Norway Identification Number -->
<Entity id="d4c8a798-e9f2-4bd3-9652-500d24080fc3" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5845">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5845">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_norway_id_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5846">Keyword_norway_id_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5846">Keyword_norway_id_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5847">Personal identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5847">Personal identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5848">Norwegian ID Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5848">Norwegian ID Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5849">ID Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5849">ID Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5850">Процедура</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5850">Identification</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5851">персоннуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5851">Personnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5852">фøдселснуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5852">Fødselsnummer</span></span>

   
## <a name="philippines-unified-multi-purpose-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5853">Идентификационный номер единой системы для различных целей Филиппины</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5853">Philippines unified multi-purpose identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5854">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5854">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5855">12 цифр, разделенных дефисами.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5855">12 digits separated by hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5856">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5856">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5857">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5857">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5858">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5858">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5859">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5859">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5860">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5860">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5861">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5861">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5862">одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5862">one digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5863">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5863">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5864">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5864">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5865">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5865">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5866">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5866">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5867">регулярное выражение Regex_philippines_unified_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5867">The regular expression Regex_philippines_unified_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5868">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_philippines_id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5868">A keyword from Keyword_philippines_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Philippines Unified Multi-Purpose ID number -->
<Entity id="019b39dd-8c25-4765-91a3-d9c6baf3c3b3" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_philippines_unified_id"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_philippines_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5869">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5869">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_philippines_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5870">Keyword_philippines_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5870">Keyword_philippines_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5871">Unified Multi-Purpose ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5871">Unified Multi-Purpose ID</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5872">умид</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5872">UMID</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5873">Identity Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5873">Identity Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5874">Pinag-isang Multi-Layunin ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5874">Pinag-isang Multi-Layunin ID</span></span>

## <a name="poland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5875">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5875">Poland driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5876">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5876">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5877">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5877">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5878">14 цифр, содержащих 2 косых черты.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5878">14 digits containing 2 forward slashes</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5879">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5879">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5880">14 цифр и 2 косых черт:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5880">14 digits and 2 forward slashes:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5881">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5881">five digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5882">косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5882">a forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5883">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5883">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5884">косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5884">a forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5885">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5885">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5886">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5886">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5887">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5887">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5888">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5888">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5889">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5889">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5890">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5890">The regular expression  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5891">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5891">A keyword from  `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5892">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5892">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_poland_eu_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5893">Keywords_poland_eu_driver "s_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5893">Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5894">DL #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5894">dl#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5895">driver license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5895">driver license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5896">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5896">driver license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5897">Лицензия на драйвер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5897">driver licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5898">Drivers лик.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5898">drivers lic.</span></span>

## <a name="poland-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5907">Идентификационная карточка Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5907">Poland identity card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5908">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5908">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5909">три буквы и шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5909">three letters and six digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5910">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5910">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5911">три буквы (без учета регистра), за которыми следуют шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5911">three letters (not case sensitive) followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5912">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5912">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5913">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5913">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5914">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5914">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5915">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5915">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5916">функция Func_polish_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5916">The function Func_polish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5917">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5917">A keyword from Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5918">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5918">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Poland Identity Card-->
<Entity id="25E64989-ED5D-40CA-A939-6C14183BB7BF" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number" />
      </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5919">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5919">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5920">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5920">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5921">Довóд особисти</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5921">Dowód osobisty</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5922">Нумер доводу особистего</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5922">Numer dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5923">Назва i нумер доводу особистего</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5923">Nazwa i numer dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5924">Назва i НР доводу особистего</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5924">Nazwa i nr dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5925">Nazwa i nr dowodu tożsamości</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5925">Nazwa i nr dowodu tożsamości</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5926">Dowód Tożsamości</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5926">Dowód Tożsamości</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5927">Dow.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5927">dow.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5928">совместим.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5928">os.</span></span>

   
## <a name="poland-national-id-pesel"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5929">Национальный идентификатор Польша (PESEL)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5929">Poland national ID (PESEL)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5930">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5930">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5931">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5931">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5932">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5932">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5933">6 цифр, представляющих дату рождения, в формате ГГММДД.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5933">6 digits representing date of birth in the format YYMMDD</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5934">4 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5934">4 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5935">1 контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5935">1 check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5936">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5936">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5937">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5937">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5938">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5938">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5939">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5939">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5940">функция Func_pesel_identification_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5940">The function Func_pesel_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5941">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_pesel_identification_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5941">A keyword from Keyword_pesel_identification_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5942">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5942">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5943">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5943">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5944">функция Func_pesel_identification_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5944">The function Func_pesel_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5945">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5945">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Poland National ID (PESEL) -->
      <Entity id="E3AAF206-4297-412F-9E06-BA8487E22456" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_pesel_identification_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_pesel_identification_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_pesel_identification_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5946">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5946">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_pesel_identification_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5947">Keyword_pesel_identification_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5947">Keyword_pesel_identification_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5948">довóд особисти</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5948">dowód osobisty</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5949">довóдособисти</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5949">dowódosobisty</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5950">ниеповтарзални нумер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5950">niepowtarzalny numer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5951">ниеповтарзалнинумер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5951">niepowtarzalnynumer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5952">НР. PESEL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5952">nr.-pesel</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5953">НР — PESEL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5953">nr-pesel</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5954">Нумер идентификацижни</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5954">numer identyfikacyjny</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5955">PESEL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5955">pesel</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5956">тоżсамоśЦи народовеж</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5956">tożsamości narodowej</span></span>

   
## <a name="poland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5957">Номер паспорта для Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5957">Poland passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5958">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5958">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5959">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5959">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5960">две буквы и семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5960">two letters and seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5961">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5961">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5962">Две буквы (без учета регистра), за которыми следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5962">Two letters (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5963">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5963">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5964">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5964">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5965">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5965">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5966">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5966">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5967">функция Func_polish_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5967">The function Func_polish_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5968">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5968">A keyword from Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5969">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5969">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Poland Passport Number -->
<Entity id="03937FB5-D2B6-4487-B61F-0F8BFF7C3517" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number" />
      </Pattern>
</Entity>
</Version>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5970">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5970">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5971">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5971">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5972">Нумер пасзпорту</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5972">Numer paszportu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5973">НР.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5973">Nr.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5974">пасзпорту</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5974">Paszportu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5975">пасзпорт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5975">Paszport</span></span>

## <a name="poland-regon-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5976">Номер РЕГОНа Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5976">Poland REGON number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5977">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5977">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5978">девять цифр или номер из 14 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5978">nine digit or 14 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5979">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5979">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5980">девять цифр или 14 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5980">nine digit or 14-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5981">девять цифр или</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5981">nine digits or</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5982">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5982">nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5983">дискрецион</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5983">hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5984">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5984">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5985">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5985">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5986">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5986">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5987">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5987">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5988">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5988">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5989">Функция Func_polish_regon_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5989">The function Func_polish_regon_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5990">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_polish_regon_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5990">A keyword from Keywords_polish_regon_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5991">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5991">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-5992">Функция Func_polish_regon_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-5992">The function Func_polish_regon_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Polish REGON Number  -->
      <Entity id="fc87b421-f437-4f8b-b739-29a735ead0d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_regon_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_polish_regon_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_regon_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="poland-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6009">Идентификационный номер для таможенного учета Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6009">Poland tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6010">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6010">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6011">11 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6011">11 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6012">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6012">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6013">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6013">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6014">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6014">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6015">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6015">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6016">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6016">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6017">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6017">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6018">Функция  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6018">The function  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6019">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6019">A keyword from  `Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
  
```xml
      <!-- Poland Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="1ff28b4d-40f2-49e9-b677-9606a88e2bca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-citizen-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6049">Номер карточки с префиксом "Португалия"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6049">Portugal citizen card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6050">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6050">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6051">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6051">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6052">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6052">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6053">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6053">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6054">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6054">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6055">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6055">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6056">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6056">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6057">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6057">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6058">регулярное выражение Regex_portugal_citizen_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6058">The regular expression Regex_portugal_citizen_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6059">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_portugal_citizen_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6059">A keyword from Keyword_portugal_citizen_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Portugal Citizen Card Number -->
<Entity id="91a7ece2-add4-4986-9a15-c84544d81ecd" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_citizen_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_portugal_citizen_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6068">Идентификация нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6068">identification no</span></span>

## <a name="portugal-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6079">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Португалия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6079">Portugal driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6080">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6080">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6081">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6081">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6082">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь чисел в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6082">two letters followed by a seven numbers in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6083">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6083">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6084">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр со специальными символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6084">two letters followed by seven numbers with special characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6085">две буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6085">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6086">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6086">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6087">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6087">six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6088">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6088">a space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6089">одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6089">one digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6090">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6090">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6091">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6091">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6092">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6092">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6093">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6093">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6094">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6094">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6095">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6095">A keyword from  `Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6111">Номер паспорта для Португалия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6111">Portugal passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6112">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6112">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6113">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6113">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6114">одна буква, за которой следуют шесть цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6114">one letter followed by six digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6115">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6115">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6116">одна буква, за которой следуют шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6116">one letter followed by six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6117">одна буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6117">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6118">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6118">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6119">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6119">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6120">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6120">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6121">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6121">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6122">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6122">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6123">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6123">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6124">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6124">A keyword from  `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6131">Идентификационный номер для налога на Португалия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6131">Portugal tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6132">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6132">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6133">девять цифр с необязательными пробелами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6133">nine digits with optional spaces</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6134">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6134">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6135">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6135">3 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6136">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6136">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6137">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6137">3 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6138">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6138">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6139">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6139">3 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6140">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6140">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6141">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6141">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6142">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6142">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6143">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6143">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6144">Функция  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6144">The function  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6145">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6145">A keyword from  `Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6146">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6146">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6147">Функция  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6147">The function  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="65372402-3131-4f1e-9983-4439841d1f15" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6172">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Румыния</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6172">Romania driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6173">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6173">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6174">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6174">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6175">один символ, за которым следуют восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6175">one character followed by eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6176">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6176">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6177">один символ, за которым следуют восемь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6177">one character followed by eight digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6178">одна буква (без учета регистра) или цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6178">one letter (not case-sensitive) or digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6179">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6179">eight digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6180">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6180">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6181">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6181">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6182">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6182">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6183">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6183">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6184">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6184">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6185">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6185">A keyword from  `Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6191">Лицензия на драйвер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6191">driver licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6192">Drivers лик.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6192">drivers lic.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6195">driver's license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6195">driver's license</span></span>

## <a name="romania-personal-numeric-code-cnp"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6201">Персональный числовой код Румыния (КНП)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6201">Romania personal numeric code (CNP)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6202">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6202">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6203">13 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6203">13 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6204">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6204">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6205">1 цифра из 1-9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6205">1 digit from 1-9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6206">6 цифр, представляющих дату рождения (ГГММДД)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6206">6 digits representing date of birth (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6207">2 цифры, которые могут быть 01-52 или 99</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6207">2 digits which can be 01-52 or 99</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6208">4 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6208">4 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6209">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6209">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6210">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6210">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6211">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6211">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6212">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6212">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6213">Функция  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6213">The function  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6214">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6214">A keyword from  `Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6215">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6215">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6216">Функция  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6216">The function  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Romania Personal Numerical Code (CNP) -->
      <Entity id="eb5fa399-fe28-4c67-8188-d63a616ed89c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6267">Номер паспорта для Румыния</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6267">Romania passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6268">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6268">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6269">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6269">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6270">восемь или девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6270">eight or nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6271">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6271">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6272">восемь или девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6272">eight or nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6273">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6273">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6274">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6274">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6275">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6275">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6276">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6276">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6277">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6277">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6278">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6278">A keyword from  `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6279">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6279">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_romania_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6280">Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6280">Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6281">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6281">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6282">номер паспорта для румынского языка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6282">romanian passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6283">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6283">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6284">нумăрул паșапортулуи</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6284">numărul pașaportului</span></span>


## <a name="russia-passport-number-domestic"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6285">Номер паспорта для России (Россия)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6285">Russia passport number domestic</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6286">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6286">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6287">номер из десяти цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6287">ten digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6288">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6288">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6289">номер из десяти цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6289">ten digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6290">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6290">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6291">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6291">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6292">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6292">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6293">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6293">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6294">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6294">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6295">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6295">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6296">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6296">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6297">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6297">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6298">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6298">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6299">Регулярное выражение Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6299">The regex Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6300">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6300">A keyword from Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Russian Passport Number Domestic -->
      <Entity id="76ec2f5d-cedb-48e1-8070-1998794af445" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="russia-passport-number-international"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6317">Номер паспорта для России Международная</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6317">Russia passport number international</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6318">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6318">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6319">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6319">nine digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6320">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6320">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6321">девять цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6321">nine digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6322">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6322">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6323">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6323">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6324">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6324">seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6325">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6325">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6326">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6326">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6327">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6327">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6328">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6328">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6329">Регулярное выражение Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_International находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6329">The regex Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_International finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6330">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6330">A keyword from Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Russian Passport Number International -->
      <Entity id="ac5f4878-75e4-4b82-af2d-02e13ea9f411" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_International" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="saudi-arabia-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6347">Национальный идентификатор для Саудовской Аравии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6347">Saudi Arabia National ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6348">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6348">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6349">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6349">ten digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6350">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6350">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6351">десять последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6351">ten consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6352">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6352">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6353">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6353">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6354">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6354">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6355">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6355">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6356">регулярное выражение Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6356">The regular expression Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6357">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6357">A keyword from Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Saudi Arabia National ID -->
<Entity id="8c5a0ba8-404a-41a3-8871-746aa21ee6c0" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6358">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6358">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6359">Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6359">Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6362">ID number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6362">ID number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6363">الوطنية الهوية بطاقة رقم</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6363">الوطنية الهوية بطاقة رقم</span></span> 

   
## <a name="singapore-national-registration-identity-card-nric-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6364">Номер национальной идентификационной карточки для регистрации (NRIC), Сингапур</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6364">Singapore national registration identity card (NRIC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6365">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6365">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6366">девять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6366">nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6367">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6367">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6368">девять букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6368">nine letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6369">буква "F", "G", "S" или "T" (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6369">the letter "F", "G", "S", or "T" (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6370">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6370">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6371">цифра алфавитной проверки</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6371">an alphabetic check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6372">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6372">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6373">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6373">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6374">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6374">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6375">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6375">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6376">регулярное выражение Regex_singapore_nric находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6376">The regular expression Regex_singapore_nric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6377">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_singapore_nric;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6377">A keyword from Keyword_singapore_nric is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6378">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6378">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6379">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6379">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6380">регулярное выражение Regex_singapore_nric находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6380">The regular expression Regex_singapore_nric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ac3f4-6381">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3f4-6381">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Singapore National Registration Identity Card (NRIC) Number -->
<Entity id="cead390a-dd83-4856-9751-fb6dc98c34da" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_singapore_nric"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_singapore_nric"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_singapore_nric"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
